  <description type="long">
    <p>QuickBib helps you quickly generate BibTeX bibliographic entries from identifiers such as DOIs and arXiv IDs. Enter an identifier and QuickBib will fetch the metadata and produce a ready-to-use BibTeX entry which you can copy to your clipboard and use in your LaTeX documents.</p>
    <p>Features include: fast DOI/arXiv lookup and copy-to-clipboard.</p>
  </description>
